


** Rollover Cables.
-- Used To Connect Switch And Router.
	
		1 to 8
		2 to 7
		3 to 6
		4 to 5
		5 to 4
		6 to 3
		7 to 2
		8 to 1



Router> enable  
used to enter privillage mode.

Router#>configure terminal
used to enter global configuration mode.

Router(config)# enable password {password}
used to configure a password to protect privillage mode.

Router(config)# service password-encryption.
encrypts the enable password ( and other password ). But Not Safe.


Router(config)# enable secret ${password}
Ecrypts The Password And Cannot Decrypt The Password. Because This Is More Safe.


Router(config)# no ${command}
removes the command

Router(config)# show running-config
displays the current,active configuration file.

Router(config)# show running-config 
displays the current configuration file.


Router(config)# show startup-config
after devices get-up this configuration is boot-up


Router(config)# write
copy running-config startup-config	
